\mt1 Fas Timoti  
\imt1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani m…ô n…ôfe i n…ôkuku…ô  
\ip N…ôkuku…ô me i Pol r…®m…ôrai, Fas m…®ne Seken Timoti m…®ne Taetas, kani m…ô n…ôkuku…ô me s…ôv…ôi pasta me, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ham…ô…°kiari ia wok m…®ne noien s…ôv…ôi pasta me. Timoti r…®n…ôtui fwe Listra. S…ôv…ônhi tata i…ôm…ô Kris, m…ôt…ô s…ôv…ônhi mama pran Isrel. S…ôv…ônhi mama ramahat…ôn in ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan ia nouihiien s…ôv…ônhi. Pol ramev…ôn mam…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Kristo. Ia nav…ônien s…ôv…ônhi s…ô ro k…ôru ir…ô Timoti rukurir…ô in. In ramasitu ia Pol ia wok s…ôv…ônhi. N…ôp…®n Pol r…®m…ôrai n…ôkuku…ô i, Timoti ramo wok r…ômwhen ia iahat…ôn m…®ne i…ôm…ô asori s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me fwe Efesas. Timoti in t…ômaru…ô riti, m…ôt…ô ruvehi wok s…ôv…ôi niriien nakalasia me. Ro pen Pol r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i rev…ôn tukwe. Ia n…ôkuku…ô i Pol ramasitu ir…ô mam…ôv…ôha…° min ia wok s…ôv…ônhi. Pol ram…ôv…ôha…° min m…ô tram…ôkeikei m…ôsiari t…® nahat…ôn eiku…ô me m…®ne nahat…ônien me s…ôv…ônraha s…ôm…ôme h…ôpw…ôh natukwatukwien. Pol rokeikei p…®k Timoti, ro pen ruvei pen n…ôv…ôha…°ien me min m…ô tr…ôfo ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in i…ôrmama riti s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Kol 1:27\x*Iou Pol. Iou aposol riti s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo. Kumwes…ôn s…ô rauvehim…®ru k…®taha m…®ne Iesu Kristo s…ô sam…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®taha ir…ô irau krouni n…ôkwanrau m…ô tako.   
\p
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Wok Me 16:1-3, Taet 1:4\x*Iakamrai n…ôkuku…ô i mik, Timoti. Ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôkrau ik…ômwhen ia n…ôr…®k p…ôrhien. Pw…ôh Tata Kumwes…ôn m…®ne Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha trou…ôriari pehe namasanien m…®ne napiien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien mik.   
\s1 Timoti tr…®nise nahat…ôn eiku…ô me  
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Fil 2:24\x*Fwe kupw…ôn, ia n…ôp…®n iak…®namev…ôn fwe profens Masetonia, n…ôn…ô, iak…®ni pehe tukw ik i m…ô tikamar…ô p…ôp…®m ia taon n…ôha Efesas. N…ôrmama nepw…®n n…ôha ik…®n hamar…ô ir…ôha kamhahat…ôn n…ôrmama ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ô rop…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien atukwatukw. M…ôt…ô ik tik…®nise ir…ôha m…ô tuh…ôpw…ôh noien noien n…ôha.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 1Tim 4:7, Taet 1:14\x*Tik…®ni pen t…® nir…ôha i m…ô tuh…ôpw…ôh n…ôt…ôr…®…° p…®kien ia kw…ôna…°ei eiku…ô me m…®ne n…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani p…®k kw…ôn…ôkwus me s…ôv…ôi kaha kupw…ôn me. N…ô…°kiariien me n…ôha kamh…ôvi pehe a n…ôvis…ôien me. Ko h…ôpkasitu mh…ô ia i…ôrmama riti m…ô tro wok s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn. Wok n…ôha n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamhahat…ôt…ô a kamho.  
\v 5 Tik…ôv…ôha…° m n…ôrmama me s…ôk…®taha m…ô ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mhokeikei ir…ôha me. Pw…ôh rer…®nraha r…ômher. Pw…ôh ir…ôha hamo a noien me s…ôm…ôme ir…ôha h…ôukur…ôn m…ô ramasan. Pw…ôh ir…ôha hahat…ôt…ô p…ôrhien ia Kumwes…ôn.  
\v 6 N…ôrmama nepw…®n h…ôn…ôpw…ôh noien me i, mh…ôn…ôti karen, mh…ôuvav…ôn t…® n…ô…°kiariien s…ô n…®pwran riw…ôn.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1Tim 6:4,20, Taet 1:10\x*Ir…ôha hokeikei p…®k nahat…ônien Loa, m…ôt…ô h…ôreirei n…®pwrai n…ôfe kamh…ôni, n…ôri au…ôr a m…ô kamh…ô…°kiari skai tukwe m…ô h…ôukur…ôn.   
\p
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Rom 7:12,16\x*K…®taha s…ôukur…ôn m…ô Loa in ramasan, m…ôt…ô n…ôrmama tuham…ôkeikei mhahat…ôn n…ôrmama ir…ô ia noien atukwatukw s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 9 K…®taha s…ôukur…ôn mwi m…ô k…®pk…ômri mh…ô Loa ram…ômak t…® n…ôkur atukwatukw me, m…ôt…ô k…ômri Loa ram…ômak t…® n…ôkur kamh…ôrui loa, m…®ne n…ôkur k…ônkapw…ônraha r…®skai, m…®ne n…ôkur h…ôpkahat…ôt…ô mh…ô ia Kumwes…ôn, m…®ne n…ôkur kamho noien …ôr…ôha, m…®ne n…ôkur h…ôpko mh…ô n…ôkur ikinan me, m…®ne n…ôkur h…ôpk…ômher mh…ô, m…®ne n…ôkur kamhousi …ôpune tata m…®ne mama s…ôv…ônraha, m…®ne n…ôkur kamhousi …ôpune n…ôrmama.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Taet 1:9\x*K…ômri Loa ram…ômak t…® n…ôrman m…®ne n…®pran s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôiri …ôpnapen ir…ôha me, m…®ne n…ôrman s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôiri atukw a ir…ôha me, m…®ne n…ôrmama kamhakres i…ôrmama m…ô tuhoslef ir…ô, m…®ne ieiku…ô me, m…®ne n…ôkur kamheiku…ô ia kwopun kam…ôkiri n…ô…°kiariien ik…®n, m…®ne n…ôkur kamho noien …ôr…ôha me nepw…®n mwi. Ou…ôh, n…®p…ôrhienien k…ômri Loa ram…ômak t…® n…ôkur kamho narimnari me pam n…ôha s…ô ram…ôrarki n…ô…°kiariien kamahat…ôn n…ôrmama ir…ô s…ô ratukwatukw.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt 1Tim 6:15\x*Kumwes…ôn in rasori mukuraan n…ôrmama kamh…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni in. N…ô…°kiariien atukwatukw n…ôha iakani ram…ômak ia n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ônhi. In r…®n…ômri pehe n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ia r…ô…°…®k, n…ôn…ô iakam…ôvisau irapw i.   
\s1 Iesu r…®napi Pol  
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Wok Me 9:15, Kal 1:15-16, 1Kor 15:9-10, Kal 1:13\x*Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha s…ô ramo iak…®skai t…® noien wok s…ôv…ônhi, iakani tanak tukwe in t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in r…®n…ôkiri iou m…ô iak…ômwhen, m…ôt…®…°ite ia nirak, m…ômri iou iakamo tukwini nari min.  
\v 13 Fwe kupw…ôn, iou i…ôrmama riti s…ô iakani …ôr…ôha n…ô…°h…®n, n…ôn…ô mamomet…ô n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi, mamousi p…®k ir…ôha. M…ôt…ô in rapi iou t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iapk…®ni mh…ô ihi n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô, n…ôn…ô, m…®reirei m…ô n…ôfe n…ôha iakamo.  
\v 14 I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha r…ôt…ô…°i irapw namasanien s…ôv…ônhi ia nirak rasori p…®k ir…ôhar nahat…ôt…ôien m…®ne nokeikeiien s…ô ruku pen t…® Iesu Kristo.   
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Luk 15:2, 19:10\x*In i n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien, n…ôn…ô, k…®taha pam tsam…ôkeikei mh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô. Iesu Kristo r…®m…ôuvehe ia t…®pr…ôn…ô i m…ô truvehim…®ru n…ôrmama …ôr…ôha me. Iou i…ôm…ô iak…ôr…ôha anan m…ôpi raka pam ir…ôha.  
\v 16 M…ôt…ô Iesu Kristo r…®napi iou m…ô iou iak…ôr…ôha anan r…ômwhen ia n…®mt…ôtien riti s…ô ramahat…ôn m…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônhi r…ôpw…ômw…®s m…®pko mh…ô sampam ramev…ôn t…® n…ôrmama …ôr…ôha me, pw…ôh n…ôrmama nepw…®n h…ôtoni mho r…ômwhen s…ô iak…®no h…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô, n…ôn…ô in truvei pen n…®m…®ruien rer…®n m…®nraha.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Rom 16:27\x*Kumwes…ôn in I…ôr…®m…ônu rer…®n. In r…®pkemh…ô mh…ô. Ko s…ôpk…ôtoni mh…ô. N…ôn…ô in …ôpa in Kumwes…ôn. Pw…ôh n…®siaien m…®ne n…ô…°n…ô…°…®niien krauev…ôn tukwe in ia nuk nuk me. Ou…ôh, pw…ôh ro iam…®nhi.   
\p
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt 1Tim 6:12, Jut 3\x*N…ô…°kiariien i iakani pehe tukw ik i t…ôkwt…ôkwuni, n…ôr…®k Timoti, r…ômwhen a ia n…ô…°kiariien me n…ôha profet me nepw…®n h…ôm…ôni ia niram fwe kupw…ôn. Tikuvehi n…ô…°kiariien me i pw…ôh hasitu ia niram ia narua…°…ônien amasan s…ô ikamarua…°…ôn ir…ô.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt 1Tim 3:9\x*Tikam…ôkeikei m…ôkwt…ômhiri …ôknek…®n nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôim, m…ôpw…ôh noien nari riti s…ô tro ik ikre…°i fwe ia rer…®m m…ô ik…®no n…ôr…ôhaien. N…ôrmama nepw…®n ho noien me nepw…®n s…ô h…ôukur…ôn m…ô r…ôr…ôha, n…ôn…ô ia noien n…ôha h…ônouraha nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônraha r…ômwhen ia n…®t…ôt…ô s…ô r…ôp…ôru…ô ia n…®maha.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt 2Tim 2:17, 2Tim 4:14, 1Kor 5:5\x*I…ôm…ô mi n…ôha Hameneus m…®ne Aleksanta irau mwi n…ôha ir…ôha m…®nraha. Iou iak…®n…ôseni raka irau m…ô krou…ômak ia r…ô…°i Setan pw…ôh krouukur…ôn m…ô trou…ôpw…ôh n…®ni …ôr…ôhaien Kumwes…ôn.   
\c 2  
\s1 N…ôv…ôha…°ien me ia n…®karen s…ôv…ôi n…ôfwakiien  
\p
\v 1 N…ôri s…ô iakokeikei m…ô takukupw…ôn m…®ni ro iam…®nhi ir…ô. Tik…ôv…ôha…° m n…ôrmama me s…ôk…®taha m…ô ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôfwaki m Kumwes…ôn t…® n…ôrmama me pam, n…ôn…ô mh…ôres in m…ô trasitu ia nir…ôha, muvei pen n…ôfe riw…ôn t…® nir…ôha. N…ôn…ô tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôni mwi tanak ramev…ôn t…® Kumwes…ôn t…® nir…ôha.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Efes 6:18, Fil 4:6\x*Ir…ôha tuh…ôfwaki t…® ki…° me m…®ne n…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôuvehi nasoriien m…ô k…®taha tsar…ô ia n…ôm…ôrinuien m…®ne nar…ôien afafa, mhar…ô ir…ô, mh…ôsiai Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô mhesi pen noien atukwatukw me.  
\v 3 Noien i ramasan n…ôn…ô n…ôp…®n Kumwes…ôn s…ôk…®taha s…ô rauvehim…®ru k…®taha tr…ôtoni rer…®n ra…°ien.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Esik 18:23, 1Tim 4:10, 2Tes 3:9, Rom 3:29-30, Hip 12:24\x*In rokeikei m…ô truvehim…®ru n…ôrmama me pam, n…ôn…ô mokeikei m…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôuvehe mh…ôukur…ôn n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 5 Kumwes…ôn kuatia a ramar…ô, n…ôn…ô, I…ôrmama kuatia a ram…ôrer ia n…®mwrhenhi Kumwes…ôn m…®ne n…ôrmama mavi s…®mw…®n ir…ôha. I…ôrmama n…ôha in n…ôha Iesu Kristo  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Kal 1:4\x*s…ô r…®m…ôuvei pehe atukw a in ia n…ôp…®n atukwatukw t…® n…ôr…ôkuien suatuk s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama me pam m…ô tr…®fi ir…ôha ia noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha. N…ôn…ô ramahat…ôn m…ô Kumwes…ôn rokeikei m…ô truvehim…®ru n…ôrmama me pam.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Wok Me 9:15, Kal 2:7-8, 2Tim 1:11\x*N…ôri in i kuvehi ut…ô iou tukwe aposol m…®ne iahat…ôn s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel m…ô tak…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan m…®nraha s…ô ram…ô…°kiari ia nahat…ôt…ôien m…®ne n…®p…ôrhienien. (Iakani p…ôrhien iapkeiku…ô mh…ô.)   
\p
\v 8 Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô iakokeikei m…ô ia kwopun me pam n…ôrman me tuh…ôuvehi ut…ô r…ô…°…®nraha r…ômher, mo ikinan i, n…ôn…ô mh…ôfwaki m Kumwes…ôn. Ir…ôha tuho iam…®nha ir…ô mh…ôpw…ôh niemaha m…®ne n…ôvis…ôien.   
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1Tes 3:3-5\x*N…ôn…ô iakokeikei m…ô n…®pran me tuharkahu ia t…®nari s…ô ratukwatukw a, r…®pko mh…ô t…®nari kavi n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrman ir…ô, u…ô t…®nari kamarkahu i kam…ôrpwi tukwe. R…ôr…ôha m…ô ho n…®mwai nukw…ônenraha m…ô tuh…ôrpwi tukwe u…ô h…ôuvehi pen mar…ômar…ô me k…®no ia kol m…®ne perel me, u…ô harkahu t…®nari n…ônimen rut…ô p…®k.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt 1Tim 5:10\x*Ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mharkahu ia noien amasan me r…ômwhen ia karkahu s…ôv…ônraha, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in i noien atukwatukw s…ô n…®pran me s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôni m…ô ir…ôha hokeikei Kumwes…ôn tuho.   
\p
\v 11 N…ôp…®n kamahat…ôn nakalasia me, pw…ôh n…®pran me hafafa mh…ôpw…ôh n…ô…°kiariien, mh…ôsiai nahat…ôn me, mh…ôuvehi nukur…ônien.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt 1Kor 14:34\x*Iou iapk…ôseni mh…ô m…ô n…®pran tuhahat…ôn u…ô h…ôr…®m…ônu ia n…ôrman. Ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mhafafa,  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Jen 2:7,22, 1Kor 11:8-9\x*t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô fwe kupw…ôn Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôkupw…ôn mo Atam kurir…ô ro If.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt 2Kor 11:3\x*N…ôn…ô r…®pko mh…ô Atam n…ô Setan r…®m…ôkupw…ôn meiku…ô ir…ô n…ôn…ô ro n…ôkwan, m…ôt…ô If r…®no n…ôkwai Setan n…ôn…ô m…ôrui n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn.  
\v 15 M…ôt…ô m…ô pran ram…ômwur pen ia nahat…ôt…ôien, m…®ne nokeikeiien, m…®ne noien s…ô r…ômher mo ikinan i, n…ôn…ô in pr…ôn afafa, n…ôp…®n ram…ômis…ô t…® t…®ni m…ô tr…ôtui, Kumwes…ôn tr…ôtui amasan tukwe muvehim…®ru in.   
\c 3  
\s1 Noien s…ôv…ôi elta me m…®ne tikon me  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Wok Me 20:28\x*In i n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrmama riti rokeikei m…ô truvehe i…ôm…ô asori s…ô ram…ôtui t…® nakalasia me, n…ôn…ô, in r…®nokeikei wok riti s…ô ramasan.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Taet 1:6-9\x*I…ôm…ô asori s…ô rauvehi wok n…ôha noien s…ôv…ônhi tram…ôkeikei mo iam…®nhi ir…ô. K…ôpw…ôh n…ôt…ôien noien …ôr…ôha riti ir…ô. In s…ôv…ônhi pran kuatia a. R…®pko mh…ô in i…ôrmama s…ô ram…ôn…®mwi p…®k, m…ôt…ô in n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônhi ram…ômak amasan ia n…ôp…®n me. In i…ôrmama s…ô kamsiai in. In i…ôrmama s…ô ram…ôsev…ôr ia rukw…ônu s…ôv…ônhi t…® n…ôrmama pw…®spw…®s me. In iahat…ôn amasan riti.  
\v 3 I…ôrmama s…ô ram…ôn…®mwi p…®k u…ô ramousi i…ôrmama ko r…®pkuvehi mh…ô wok i. M…ôt…ô i…ôrmama s…ô noien s…ôv…ônhi ramasan m…ôpou, r…ôpw…ôh n…ôvis…ôien, m…®pkokeikei p…®k mh…ô mane, in rukur…ôn nuvehiien wok i.  
\v 4 In tram…ôkeikei miri amasan n…ôrmama kamhar…ô ia n…ôkwai nimw…ô s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô mo n…®pwn…ôt…®n me tuh…ôsiai in mho n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 5 Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrmama riti r…®reirei niri amasanien n…ôrmama kamhar…ô ia n…ôkwai nimw…ô s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô, tr…ôfo miri amasan nakalasia me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn? In r…®reirei noien.  
\v 6 I…ôrmama rahat…ôt…ô vi a ia Iesu r…®pk…ômwhen mh…ô m…ô truvehi wok i kamo r…ôrpwi tukwe m…®mwei pen ia n…ôr…ôhaien s…ô Setan r…®no n…ôn…ô Kumwes…ôn r…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt 2Kor 8:21\x*R…ômwhen a mwi i…ôrmama s…ô rauvehi wok iam…®nhi n…ôrmama me fwe iru…ô tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôni amasan in kamo in r…®mwei pen ia kw…ônkru s…ôv…ôi Setan n…ôn…ô k…®ni …ôr…ôha in.   
\p
\v 8 Ia noien a mwi n…ôha tikon me noien s…ôv…ônraha tram…ôkeikei mo iam…®nhi ir…ô. Ir…ôha n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamsiai ir…ôha. N…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônraha r…®pko mh…ô k…ôru. H…ôpk…ôn…®mwi p…®k mh…ô n…ôn…®mwiien skai r…ômwhen ia waen. Ir…ôha h…ôpkokeikei p…®k mh…ô mane.  
\v 9 Ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôkwt…ômhiri noien s…ôv…ôi nahat…ôt…ôien Kumwes…ôn r…®no pui pehe ia n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha s…ô r…ômher.  
\v 10 N…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme hokeikei m…ô tuh…ôuvehi wok s…ôv…ôi tikon, nakalasia me tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôkupw…ôn mh…ôt…ô amasan ir…ôha. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô h…ôpk…ôt…ô mh…ô noien …ôr…ôha riti ia nir…ôha, n…ôn…ô, ir…ôha h…ôukur…ôn nuvehiien wok n…ôha.   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Taet 2:3\x*Ia noien a mwi n…ôha n…®pran me s…ôv…ôi tikon me\f + \fr 3:11 \ft Suatuk riti mwi t…® nuvsiniien n…ô…°kiariien i ro iam…®nhi ir…ô. ‚ÄúIa noien a mwi n…ôha, tikon n…®pran me noien s…ôv…ônraha tram…ôkeikei mo iam…®nhi ir…ô. Ir…ôha n…®pran me s…ôm…ôme kamsiai ir…ôha. R…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…®pran me s…ôv…ôi n…®niien n…®kare i…ôrmama u…ô n…®pran me s…ôv…ôi n…ôn…®mwiien, m…ôt…ô ir…ôha n…®pran s…ôm…ôme n…ôrmama h…ôukur…ôn n…ôt…®…°iteien ia nir…ôha ia narimnari me pam.‚Äù\f* noien s…ôv…ônraha tram…ôkeikei mo iam…®nhi ir…ô. Ir…ôha n…®pran me s…ôm…ôme kamsiai ir…ôha. R…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha n…®pran me s…ôv…ôi n…®niien n…®kare i…ôrmama u…ô n…®pran me s…ôv…ôi n…ôn…®mwiien, m…ôt…ô ir…ôha n…®pran me s…ôm…ôme n…ôrmama h…ôukur…ôn n…ôt…®…°iteien ia nir…ôha ia narimnari me pam.   
\p
