\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Lev 19:32\x*Tik…ôpw…ôh n…ô…°kiari skaiien m n…ôr…°har…ô me, m…ôt…ô tik…ô…°kiari amasan m…®nraha r…ômwhen m…ô ir…ôha tata me s…ôim. Tik…ô…°kiari m nt…ômaru…ô me r…ômwhen m…ô ir…ôha piam me,  
\v 2 m…ô…°kiari m n…®pr…ônem…ô me r…ômwhen m…ô ir…ôha mama me s…ôim. Tik…ô…°kiari m n…®pran vi me r…ômwhen m…ô ir…ôha k…®tirimam me. N…ô…°kiariien s…ô tik…®ni pen t…® nir…ôha i tram…ôkeikei matukwatukw pam m…ômher.   
