\v 15 \x - \xo 6:15 \xt Dut 10:17, Rev 17:14\x*Nuveheien s…ôv…ônhi Kumwes…ôn tro rier pehe ia n…ôp…®n atukwatukw s…ôv…ônhi. In Kumwes…ôn s…ô kam…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni in. In …ôpa ram…ôr…®m…ônu ia narimnari me pam. In Ki…° s…ô rasori ia ki…° me. N…ôn…ô in I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ô rasori ia n…ôr…®m…ônu me.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Eks 33:20\x*In …ôpa r…®pkemh…ô mh…ô mamar…ô rer…®n ia kwopun riti rukuraan ik…®n, n…ôn…ô, i…ôrmama riti ko r…®pkev…ôn mh…ô ipaka. I…ôrmama riti r…®pk…ôtoni raka mh…ô in, n…ôn…ô, t…®pk…ôtoni mh…ô mwi. Pw…ôh n…®siaiien m…®ne n…ôr…®m…ônuien s…ô tr…®pkiw…ôn mh…ô krauev…ôn tukwe in. Ou…ôh, pw…ôh ro iam…®nhi.   
